name: MobileNetV3-Small for Image Classification
full_description: MobileNetV3-Small is a lightweight convolutional neural network architecture optimized for mobile and embedded vision applications. It is part of the MobileNetV3 family, which balances latency, accuracy, and model size using advanced techniques like neural architecture search and platform-aware network design. MobileNetV3-Small is specifically tailored for devices with limited computational resources, enabling real-time image classification tasks with high efficiency.
keywords: image classification, deep learning, MobileNetV3, mobile networks, efficient neural networks, lightweight models
author: Eve Martinez

ai_model.name: MobileNetV3-Small
ai_model.description: A lightweight convolutional neural network model designed for efficient image classification on mobile and embedded devices.
